He chooses to capitalizes random words in the middle of a sentence while sometimes ignoring words that start them. Sometimes he falls in love with his commas or forgets that the period even exists.
Almost everything reads like stream of consciousness which if I had to put money on anything is exactly what it is and how he can be so productive.
